data.description: Welcome Home to this  lovely home in River's Edge; a 55+ gated community.  Featuring a 2 bedroom, 2 bath and a den with 1610 sf.   An en-suite bedroom with vaulted ceiling, slider to the patio, walk-in closet, dual sinks, soaking tub separate  shower. and enclosed toilet.  Sunny and bright kitchen with garden window,  snack bar, walk-in pantry, tile counters, gas cooktop and dining area with slider to the patio.  All appliances included.  Great room with gas fireplace will be so cozy and warm.  Split floor plan with guest bedroom, office/den and bath with tub/shower.  An attached two car garage with an abundance of storage cabinets.  Common area with picnic table and trail down to the River.  RV parking upon availability.  HOA takes care of front  yard landscaping, water/sewer and common area.  Come and enjoy this care free living.  Rhinehart Park is right down and the street and is perfect for a stroll.  Convenient location; close to shopping and hospital.  Don't miss this one.
